<section>
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
        Danfillo Cassava Processing and Animal Feeds is an agribusiness based in Jigawa State, Nigeria.
        We process locally grown cassava into food products and affordable animal feed, helping farmers
        reduce losses, increase income, and promote peaceful coexistence between farmers and herders.
    </p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Buy cassava directly from smallholder farmers</li>
        <li>Process cassava into flour and feed ingredients</li>
        <li>Produce affordable animal feed for livestock farmers and herders</li>
        <li>Reduce post-harvest losses and market exploitation</li>
    </ul>
</section>

<section>
